data.description: Step inside of this charming home conveniently located to Historic Downtown Statesville, I-40, and I-77.  Upon entering, you are greeted by the cozy living area and open floor plan. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is in a great location with no HOA!  The primary bedroom offers a generous sized walk in closet and spacious bathroom.  Outside, the large fenced in yard is magnified with beautiful landscaping and plenty of room for that outdoor oasis you have always wanted.  Relax on your private back patio and escape in a good book after a long day.
